{"tid":2283022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【簽爆佢唔該】 支持民間改劃，剎停明日大嶼填海！","createTime":"2020-11-12T09:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T02:24:11.000Z","uid":316578,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fee72fa0a61cad949044ec573b0c9514d5bd1629","tid":2283022,"uid":316578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://www.supporthk.org/?petition=%E9%82%84%E6%B5%B7%E6%96%BC%E6%B5%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.supporthk.org%2F%3Fpetition%3D%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%25B5%25B7&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BypUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=c1766a97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.supporthk.org/?petition=%E9%82%84%E6%B5%B7%E6%96%BC%E6%B5%B7</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nc75E10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNc75E10.jpg&h=913dd3e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早排有位坪洲居民自己向城規會入咗改劃申請，將大嶼山中部水域主要劃作「貨櫃碼頭」用途嘅區域，改劃作「海洋功能保留區」。（係呀，本來十幾廿年前董生諗住擴建埋做貨櫃碼頭，但最後無做到，仲係個海）🏝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰個位剛好同政府諗住大推嘅「明日大嶼」範圍有重疊，所以個改劃申請變相係衝擊緊「明日大嶼」計劃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n⚠️個改劃申請今個星期五（11月13日）截止收公眾意見‼️暫定出年1月8日上城規會審議。與其問做來仲有咩用，不如問自己仲有無嘗試過其他方法聚民氣去反對明日大嶼？<br />\n<br />\n有心團體在SupportHK整咗個template俾大家填，頂頭條link <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />click「簽名撐」後，如果大家同意所寫嘅理據，其實填個名+揀晒啲理據+最後click個掣「簽名撐」就搞掂（系統會直接幫你送埋封電郵去城規會！）<br />\n<br />\n民間改劃申請（編號 Y/I-NEL/1)：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/Y_I-NEL_1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Ftpb%2Ftc%2Fplan_application%2FY_I-NEL_1.html&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BypUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=7ac8b182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: